OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy across Scotland,
OL,6,Fwith showery rain developing at times.
OL,7,FGenerally sunny elsewhere, but the
OL,8,Frisk of low cloud along eastern coasts
OL,9,Fof England. Breezy in the south. Hot
OL,10,Fin the west, cooler in the east.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FPatchy rain easing across
OL,13,FScotland. Low cloud becoming more
OL,14,Fextensive across central and eastern
OL,15,Fareas, with clear spells remaining in
OL,16,Fthe west. A warm night, but windy in
OL,17,Fthe south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
