OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FLow cloud will quickly burn
OL,6,Fback to the coasts to leave plenty of
OL,7,Fsunshine, though it may tend to remain
OL,8,Fcloudier across Scotland. Windy in the
OL,9,Fsouth. Very warm.
